reviewText: These films are worth a second look. Especially good is Angie starring Geena Davis. This is a very good movie. The others are fairly good as well but this one alone is worth the price.
All 6 of these movies with these GREAT LEADIND LADIES are TERRIFIC!!! - BUY THIS NOW!!!!!

Lovely to get 6 movies in a box.  Would have been nice if all the movies were new.  One disc of the four arrived scratched.  We did not open the box right away and missed the reurn date.  Good deal?  I don't think so.  On the other hand, it wasn't an expensive set.
How can you go wrong with so many stars in some really entertaining movies.
Great collection of Bette Midler movies and other funny films, it was a Christmas present for my mom and she loved it.
Perfect or when you're home sick and needed a good cheer-me-up session!
I bought this set for a fundraiser --a leisure basket of items -- in honor of our AAUW movie group.
I have a couple of favorite movies in this collection

Wonderful, fun, entertainment! Well worth the price and great shows to watch over and over again. Great value and convenience having them in the same package.
